text: Delta () is a rural locality (a settlement) in Buzansky Selsoviet, Krasnoyarsky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 72 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 32 km from Astrakhan, 27 km from Krasny Yar. == References == Category:Rural localities in Krasnoyarsky District, Astrakhan Oblast
title: Delta, Astrakhan Oblast
